### 1. Register a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testpassword123",
    "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 2. Login to get Token (Chỉ cho phép Email)
# @name login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test_unique@example.com",
    "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Store access token from login response
# Chạy request 'login' hoặc 'login_email' trước khi gọi các API bên dưới
@token = {{login.response.body.access}}

### 3. Get Current User Profile (Me)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3b. List all Users (Admin/Auth)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3c. Get specific User Profile
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create a new Role (Admin only/Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/roles/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Manager"
}

### 5. List all Roles
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/roles/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Assign Role to User
# Thay đổi user_id và role_id tương ứng từ database
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/1/assign-role/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Check if Email is already registered
# Endpoint này dùng POST để bạn nhập Email vào Body cho dễ
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/check-email/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "bophat9420@gmail.com"
}
